---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import { SITE_AUTHOR, SITE_DESCRIPTION, SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={`策略框架 | ${SITE_TITLE}`} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
    <style>
      .intro { padding: 3rem 0 1rem; max-width: 900px; }
      .intro p { color: rgb(var(--gray)); font-size: 1.14rem; }
      .weight-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr)); gap: 1rem; margin: 1.5rem 0 2.5rem; }
      .weight { padding: 1.1rem; }
      .weight strong { display: block; font-size: 1.5rem; margin: 0.25rem 0; }
      .two-col { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1rem; margin: 1rem 0 2rem; }
      .card { padding: 1.25rem; }
      .card h2, .card h3 { margin-top: 0; }
      .flow { display: grid; gap: 0.75rem; margin: 1rem 0 2rem; }
      .flow-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 170px 1fr; gap: 1rem; align-items: start; padding: 0.95rem 1rem; border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 14px; background: var(--paper); }
      @media (max-width: 820px) { .weight-grid, .two-col, .flow-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <section class="intro">
        <span class="pill pill-red">由 {SITE_AUTHOR} 维护</span>
        <h1>ETF罗盘策略框架</h1>
        <p>站点现在以ETF罗盘为主系统：罗盘负责左侧动作与关键位，趋势风控负责市场确认和风险过滤，盘后复盘解释信号迁移。个股分析保留为历史归档，主线聚焦ETF。</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>罗盘状态库</h2>
        <div class="flow">
          <div class="flow-row"><span class="pill pill-red">候场库</span><p>低吸观察池，重点看弱20日基础、回踩承接、收盘位置和隔日确认。</p></div>
          <div class="flow-row"><span class="pill pill-red">伏击</span><p>从候场库晋级，代表真正伏击/持有观察动作。</p></div>
          <div class="flow-row"><span class="pill pill-green">止盈观察</span><p>来自伏击库，进入止盈观察，重点看位置打满、冲高滞涨和高位强势。</p></div>
          <div class="flow-row"><span class="pill pill-green">兑现</span><p>从伏击库晋级，代表兑现/减仓动作。</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>A股复盘评分权重</h2>
        <div class="weight-grid">
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">动量</span><strong>25%</strong><p>近3日强度，代表短线情绪。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">趋势</span><strong>20%</strong><p>近5日强度，代表趋势延续。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">资金</span><strong>20%</strong><p>主力净流入和承接力度。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">收盘</span><strong>15%</strong><p>收盘价在日内区间的位置。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill">量能</span><strong>10%</strong><p>成交额相对前5日均值。</p></div>
          <div class="weight card"><span class="pill pill-amber">新闻</span><strong>10%</strong><p>政策催化、监管关注和溢价风险。</p></div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="two-col">
        <div class="card">
          <h2>三类机会</h2>
          <h3>低位伏击</h3>
          <p>候场库里的弱势回踩品种，等待收盘确认和隔日承接。</p>
          <h3>持有兑现</h3>
          <p>伏击库里的高位强势品种，靠近目标价后分批兑现。</p>
          <h3>轮动迁移</h3>
          <p>红转绿、绿转红和准备态晋级动作，是命中率复盘的核心样本。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <h2>复盘方法</h2>
          <ol>
            <li>记录罗盘预测与盘中推荐。</li>
            <li>收盘后拉取实际涨跌幅和位置。</li>
            <li>统计候场 → 伏击、止盈观察 → 兑现的迁移。</li>
            <li>检查新闻遗漏、资金背离、高位过热和低位补跌。</li>
            <li>更新下一轮罗盘权重。</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="notice">
        <strong>A股内容同步约定</strong>
        <p>预测、盘中修正和收盘复盘进入正式结论后，同步写入ETF罗盘或A股复盘；首页跟随最新交易窗口更新。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="notice">
        <strong>数据与适用范围</strong>
        <p>核心观察池为71只A股ETF/LOF，历史评价优先使用前复权（qfq）；数据源暂缺qfq时启用明确标记的未复权短窗备用。页面分别披露口径、适用交易日、数据截止时间和当前版本，并保留最近成功快照。</p>
      </section>

      <section class="notice">
        <strong>免责声明</strong>
        <p>本站内容为 {SITE_AUTHOR} 的个人研究和策略复盘，不构成任何投资建议。市场行情、资金与新闻数据可能存在延迟、缺失或错误；历史表现不代表未来收益。任何交易决策及损失均由使用者自行承担。</p>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
